  May Edochie, the first wife of Nollywood actor, Yul has yanked off her wedding ring, months after the controversial marriage of her husband to his colleague, Judy Austin. Recall that earlier this year, Yul Edochie got the social media agog when he announced his marriage to Judy and the arrival of their son, Star Dikeh. Although May has remained silent on the issue but has continued to use her newfound fame to make money. Taking to her Instagram page, May shared a video of herself advertising a product and a check on her fingers shows she had removed her wedding ring. <picture class="aligncenter wp-image-540384 size-full"><source type="image/webp" srcset="https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM.png.webp 804w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-300x300.png.webp 300w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-150x151.png.webp 150w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-768x772.png.webp 768w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-80x80.png.webp 80w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-96x96.png.webp 96w" sizes="(max-width: 804px) 100vw, 804px"><img loading="lazy" src="https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM.png" alt width="804" height="808" srcset="https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM.png 804w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-300x300.png 300w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-150x151.png 150w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/07/Screen-Shot-2022-07-09-at-9.34.35-AM-768x772.png 768w, https://www.naijanews.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/